<item>
            <title>[HBASE-8754] Log the client IP/port of the balancer invoker</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8754</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s no way for any ops to answer today: &quot;Who turned off/on the balancer?&quot;. All the logs print is the state when the RPC call is invoked, nothing else.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given this is a critical piece of admin functionality, we should log the IP for it at least.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12653142">HBASE-8754</key>
            <summary>Log the client IP/port of the balancer invoker</summary>
