                            <comment id="13704243" author="stack" created="Wed, 10 Jul 2013 05:56:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Any ideas on how might do this?  I took a looksee and client and port stuff is left behind in rpcserver and not available up in the server when balancer goes to run.  I suppose could try and pass it in in a little handbag attached to the current thread, a thread local?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13741923" author="qwertymaniac" created="Fri, 16 Aug 2013 05:13:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure of how HBase manages audit log events but in HDFS we use the UGI object associated with the call: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hadoop-common/blob/release-2.0.5-alpha/hadoop-hdfs-project/hadoop-hdfs/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/hdfs/server/namenode/FSNamesystem.java#L5270&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/hadoop-common/blob/release-2.0.5-alpha/hadoop-hdfs-project/hadoop-hdfs/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/hdfs/server/namenode/FSNamesystem.java#L5270&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13743142" author="stack" created="Sun, 18 Aug 2013 04:51:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the hint &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=qwertymaniac&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;qwertymaniac&quot;&gt;Harsh J&lt;/a&gt;  There is a RequestContext thread local that has the info.  See what you think of the 1-line patch.  I can commit if it looks good to you.  It seems to do the trick.  Here is what shows in logs if I do enable true true, false:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1122 2013-08-17 21:50:15,638 INFO  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RpcServer.handler=4,port=57158&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; master.HMaster: BalanceSwitch=true set by stack&lt;br/&gt;
1123 2013-08-17 21:50:16,695 INFO  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RpcServer.handler=7,port=57158&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; master.HMaster: BalanceSwitch=true set by stack&lt;br/&gt;
1124 2013-08-17 21:50:19,175 INFO  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RpcServer.handler=10,port=57158&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; master.HMaster: BalanceSwitch=false set by stack&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13743149" author="qwertymaniac" created="Sun, 18 Aug 2013 05:28:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If we also have a client IP, can we log that too? Helps tracing out the source better. Other than that, this looks much better than the previous message.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks a ton!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13743160" author="stack" created="Sun, 18 Aug 2013 06:23:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Let me add the address.  It is available.  Let me add this log to all admin functions, not just this balance switch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13747326" author="stack" created="Thu, 22 Aug 2013 07:12:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added logging of &apos;client&apos; &amp;#8211; their name and their inetaddress &amp;#8211; to each of the admin commands on Master.  Made all logging INFO level .  Logs look like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2013-08-22 00:08:53,994 INFO  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RpcServer.handler=24,port=50246&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; master.HMaster: Client=stack//192.168.1.129 disable xyz&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Above is disable of table &apos;xyz&apos; by &apos;client&apos; stack.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13747443" author="qwertymaniac" created="Thu, 22 Aug 2013 11:21:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The new patch looks great to me - thanks again Stack! I focussed on the replacements and perhaps the additional information in the below (&quot;running balancer&quot;) may still be useful to keep around:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
-      LOG.info(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Added move plan &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + rp + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;, running balancer&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
+      LOG.info(getClientIdAuditPrefix() + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; move &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + rp);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
